		<section class="content">
			<p class="text-white para">HSBC aims to be where the growth is, helping businesses to thrive and economies to prosper and enabling people to realise their ambitions. HSBC Group Chief Executive Stuart Gulliver outlines the Group's strategy and purpose.</p>
            <a class="btn-default our-objectives" title="Connecting customers to opportunities" href="/news-and-insight/2014/connecting-customers-to-opportunities?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hb1.1_IRQ2_On">Read more<span class="arrow"></span></a>
