	<span class="notch"></span>
	<h2 class="title text-white">
        <a title="News and insight" href="/news-and-insight?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hn1.1_On">
            News and insight
        </a>
    </h2>
    <div class="news-feature">
        <div class="lead-feature">
            
                <a href="/news-and-insight/2015/a-future-based-on-trade?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hn2.0_On" title="">
                    <noscript>
        <img src="~/media/HSBC-com/homepage/images/a-future-based-on-trade-460x258.jpg" alt="" width="460" height="258" />
    </noscript><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-original-width="460" data-original-height="258" width="460" height="258" class="lazy-momo " data-src="~/media/HSBC-com/homepage/images/a-future-based-on-trade-460x258.jpg" />



                </a>
                
        </div>
        <div class="secondary-block">
            <div class="second-feature first">
                
            <h3>
                <a href="/news-and-insight/2015/a-future-based-on-trade?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hn3.1_On" title="A future based on trade">A future based on trade</a>
            </h3>

<p class="dateStamp">
   19 Feb 2015
</p>
<p>US exports have more than doubled in a decade, reaching USD2.28 trillion in 2013. Trade in goods and services have become more diverse, helped by the dynamism of some of the nation’s major cities.<br />
<a href="/news-and-insight/2015/a-future-based-on-trade?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hn3.2_On" class="page-link">Read more<span class="screen-reader-only">about A future based on trade</span><span class="arrow"></span></a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="second-feature">
                
            <h3>
                <a href="/news-and-insight/2015/can-india-match-up?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hn3.1_On" title="Can India match up?">Can India match up?</a>
            </h3>

<p class="dateStamp">
   03 Feb 2015
</p>
<p>India is the only economy that may eventually be able to equal China's punch. In size and per-capita income, the Indian economy is where China's was in the early 2000s.
<br/>



<a href="/news-and-insight/2015/can-india-match-up?WT.ac=HGHQ_Hn3.2_On" class="page-link">Read more<span class="screen-reader-only">about Can India match up?</span><span class="arrow"></span></a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    

     
