<article class="home-black-block bg-pure-black">
	<span class="notch"></span>
	<h2 class="title text-white">
        <a title="About HSBC" href="/about-hsbc?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha1.1_On">
            About HSBC
        </a>
    </h2>
	<section class="highlights-wrapper">
		<div class="highlights">
<p class="highlights-title"><span class="text-red">6,200</span> offices</p>
<p class="highlights-title"><span class="text-red">74</span> countries and territories</p>
<p class="highlights-title"><span class="text-red">52m</span>&nbsp;customers</p>
</div>
<div class="about-hsbc">
<p class="para text-white">Headquartered in London, HSBC is one of the world&rsquo;s largest banking and financial services organisations.</p>
<a href="/about-hsbc?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha1.2_On" class="page-link text-white" title="About HSBC">About HSBC</a> </div>
	</section>
    <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="LoadMoreAboutUs" class="btn-default read-more-mobile" title="Load more news and insight stories">More About HSBC stories</a>
	<section class="home-sustainability">
		<div id="contentplaceholder_0_aboutplaceholder_0_SustainabilityImageContainer" class="sustainability-img">
			
            <noscript>
        <img src="~/media/HSBC-com/homepage/images/focusing-on-ability-960x380.jpg" alt="Focusing on ability" width="940" height="380" />
    </noscript><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-original-width="940" data-original-height="380" width="940" height="380" alt="Focusing on ability" class="lazy-momo " data-src="~/media/HSBC-com/homepage/images/focusing-on-ability-960x380.jpg" />



		</div>
		
		<div class="sustainability-module bg-white">
			<!--<h3><a href="/citizenship?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.1_On" class="title-link text-red" title="Citizenship">in <span class="bold">Citizenship</span><span class="red-arrow"></span></a></h3>-->

<h3>
<a href="/citizenship?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.1_On" class="title-link text-red" title="Citizenship
">in <span class="bold">Citizenship<span class="red-arrow"></span></span></a></h3>


<h4 class="sustainability-title text-pure-black"><a href="/news-and-insight/2014/focusing-on-ability?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.2_On" title="Focusing on ability ">Focusing on ability </a></h4>

<p class="sustainability-para">HSBC believes that making the most of the skills and talents of all employees helps the bank to serve its customers more effectively. 
 </p>
<p class="sustainability-para space-bottom">Four employees with a disability have shared their stories about working at HSBC in Brazil.
 </p>


<!--<p><strong><a title="Focusing on ability" class="link-video" href="/news-and-insight/2014/focusing-on-ability">Read more<span class="red-arrow"></span></a></strong></p>-->

<!--<a href="/citizenship/sustainability?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.1_On" class="title-link text-red" title="Sustainability">in <span class="bold">Sustainability</span><span class="red-arrow"></span></a>
<h4 class="sustainability-title text-pure-black"><a href="/citizenship/sustainability/hsbc-water-programme?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.2_On" originalAttribute="href" originalPath="/citizenship/sustainability/hsbc-water-programme?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.2_On" title="HSBC Water Programme ">HSBC Water Programme </a></h4>
<p class="sustainability-para">HSBC has created a five-year programme focused on water provision, protection and education. </p>
<p class="sustainability-para space-bottom">The partnership with Earthwatch, WaterAid and WWF will provide safe water to 1.1 million people and sanitation for 1.9 million people in South Asia and West Africa and protect freshwater ecosystems and resources in the Yangtze, Ganges, Mekong, Pantanal and African Rift Valley. </p>--><!--<a class="page-link text-black" title="Water Programme: changing lives" href="/news-and-insight/2013/water-programme-changing-lives?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.3_On" originalAttribute="href" originalPath="/news-and-insight/2013/water-programme-changing-lives?WT.ac=HGHQ_Ha2.3_On">Read more about how the programme is changing lives</a>--><!--<p><a class="page-link text-pure-black">Watch the video</a></p>-->
		</div>
	</section>
</article>
    
